 Host Discovery using Nmap (MITRE ATT&CK T1018)

## Objective

The objective of this lab was to understand how attackers perform host discovery on a network and how defenders can investigate this activity. A host discovery scan was performed from a Kali Linux machine against a Windows 10 virtual machine while monitoring the environment using Wazuh.

---

