| Component        | Description                         |
| ---------------- | ----------------------------------- |
| Hypervisor       | VirtualBox                          |
| Attacker Machine | Kali Linux                          |
| Victim Machine   | Windows 10                          |
| SIEM             | Wazuh Server                        |
| Monitoring Agent | Wazuh Agent installed on Windows 10 |

